name: DMM Alpha Trad Quickdraw (6 Pack)
description: A six-pack of Alpha Trad draws to start or add to your trad or alpine rack. The shape  is easy to handle even when wearing gloves. Their clean nose won't snag when clipping or unclipping.Grippy backbone, so you're less likely to fumble the tricky clips.Strong, lightweight I-Beam construction.Notchless nose design won't snag on gear or ropes.
